    "description_long": "This is a classic green convertible car with a vintage design, featuring a long, flat hood and a compact rear. The car has two rows of plaid-patterned seats, with the front seats separated by a central gear shift. The windshield is upright and clear, with no visible roof, emphasizing its open-top nature. The wheels are white-walled with chrome hubcaps, adding to the retro aesthetic. Chrome accents are visible on the front grille, bumpers, and side mirrors, while the rear features simple tail lights and a small trunk. The overall build suggests a mid-20th-century American or European convertible, ideal for leisurely city drives.",
